Accelstepper.zip - This is the latest accelstepper library with modifications for setBacklash(). You will find all the additional code is in clearly defined blocks starting with the comment 'start backlash' and ending with the comment 'end backlash'. If a new library is released simply search this library for the backlash code and re-insert it into the new library at the correct points.

DCC_Decoder_master - required DCC decoding library, re-published here for completenes.

PCB instructions.pdf - a pdf outlining the fuctionality of the board I designed.